presentationColumns.name: Order Line Dist Functional Amount
presentationColumns.description:
Calculate Qty:
CASE WHEN  "SSYS"."Dim - Item"."User Item Type" in ('FRT','XXOBJ_PP') THEN  "SSYS"."Dim - Sale Order Line"."Unit Selling Price"
WHEN (SIGN ("SSYS"."Dim - Sale Order Line"."Ordered Quantity") =-1) OR (SIGN ("SSYS"."Dim - Sale Order Line"."Unit Selling Price") =-1) OR ("SSYS"."Dim - Sale Order Header"."Average Discount (Varchar)"  IS NULL) OR ("SSYS"."Dim - Sale Order Header"."Average Discount (Varchar)"  ='Total list price amount equal 0') THEN "SSYS"."Dim - Sale Order Line"."Unit Selling Price" *   "SSYS"."Dim - Sale Order Line"."Ordered Quantity" 
ELSE "SSYS"."Dim - Sale Order Line"."Price List Dist" * "SSYS"."Dim - Sale Order Header"."Average Discount Multiplier" *   "SSYS"."Dim - Sale Order Line"."Ordered Quantity" 
END
presentationColumns.sourceLogicalColumn: logicalColumn:SSYS.Fact - Sale Order line.Order Line Dist Functional Amount
